<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <meta name="description" content="Honda Türkiye - The Power of Dreams. Otomobil, motosiklet, motor teknolojileri ve tarihçe.">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#cc0000">
    <title>Honda | The Power of Dreams</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/38/Honda.svg/960px-Honda.svg.png">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --honda-red: #cc0000;
            --honda-red-dark: #990000;
            --honda-red-glow: #ff1a1a;
            --black: #0a0a0a;
            --black-light: #121212;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --off-white: #fafafa;
            --gray: #7f8c8d;
            --light-gray: #ecf0f1;
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            --transition-smooth: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
            --transition-bounce: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.68, -0.55, 0.265, 1.55);
            --box-shadow-card: 0 20px 35px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            --box-shadow-glow: 0 0 25px rgba(204,0,0,0.4);
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background: var(--white);
            color: #1e2a36;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        /* Custom Scrollbar */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 10px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: var(--black); }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--honda-red); border-radius: 10px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #ff3333; }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.95);
            padding: 16px 8%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            position: fixed;
            width: 100%;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 2000;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--honda-red);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        nav.scrolled { padding: 10px 8%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.98); box-shadow: 0 5px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }

        .logo {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
            color: var(--white);
            font-size: 1.9rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: var(--transition-bounce);
            animation: logoPulse 2s infinite;
        }
        .logo:hover { transform: scale(1.05); text-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--honda-red); }
        .logo span { color: var(--honda-red); }

        @keyframes logoPulse {
            0%, 100% { text-shadow: 0 0 0px var(--honda-red); }
            50% { text-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--honda-red); }
        }

        .nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 32px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .nav-links li a {
            color: var(--white);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
            position: relative;
        }
        .nav-links li a::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--honda-red);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .nav-links li a:hover::before,
        .nav-links li a.active-nav::before { width: 100%; }
        .nav-links li a:hover,
        .nav-links li a.active-nav { color: var(--honda-red); }

        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            nav { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; padding: 12px 5%; }
            .nav-links { justify-content: center; gap: 18px; }
            .nav-links li a { font-size: 0.7rem; }
        }
        @media (max-width: 550px) { .nav-links { gap: 12px; } .nav-links li a { font-size: 0.6rem; } }

        /* Page Transitions */
        .page-content {
            display: none;
            padding-top: 100px;
            min-height: 100vh;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.7s ease forwards;
        }
        .page-content.active { display: block; }
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .container { padding: 60px 8%; max-width: 1600px; margin: 0 auto; }
        
        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 70px;
            position: relative;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a, var(--honda-red));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
        }
        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            width: 100px;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--honda-red), #ff6a6a);
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -20px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            border-radius: 4px;
            animation: pulseWidth 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulseWidth {
            0%, 100% { width: 100px; opacity: 1; }
            50% { width: 140px; opacity: 0.7; }
        }

        .sub-heading {
            font-family: 'Orbitron', monospace;
            font-size: 1.7rem;
            color: var(--honda-red);
            margin: 50px 0 30px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-left: 6px solid var(--honda-red);
            padding-left: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero-bg-img {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            z-index: 1;
            animation: slowZoom 25s infinite alternate;
        }
        @keyframes slowZoom {
            0% { transform: scale(1); }
            100% { transform: scale(1.1); }
        }
        .hero-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at center, rgba(0,0,0,0.4) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.85) 100%);
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron';
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 8vw, 5.5rem);
            letter-spacing: 6px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            z-index: 3;
            animation: glitchText 3s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes glitchText {
            0%, 100% { text-shadow: 2px 0 red, -2px 0 blue; }
            25% { text-shadow: -3px 0 red, 3px 0 blue; }
            50% { text-shadow: 3px 0 red, -3px 0 blue; }
            75% { text-shadow: -2px 0 red, 2px 0 blue; }
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            z-index: 3;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            padding: 8px 25px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }
        .hero button {
            z-index: 3;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--honda-red), #ff4444);
            border: none;
            padding: 16px 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-family: 'Orbitron';
            font-size: 1rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 50px;
            margin-top: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(204,0,0,0.4);
            transition: 0.3s;
            color: white;
        }
        .hero button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 35px rgba(204,0,0,0.6);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        /* History */
        .history-item {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 60px;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 100px;
        }
        .history-item img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 20px 20px 0 var(--honda-red);
            transition: var(--transition-bounce);
        }
        .history-item img:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 25px 25px 0 #990000;
        }
        .history-item:nth-child(even) { direction: rtl; }
        .history-item:nth-child(even) .text-box { direction: ltr; }
        .text-box {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            padding: 35px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
        .text-box h3 {
            font-family: 'Orbitron';
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--honda-red);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .text-box p { line-height: 1.7; color: #2c3e50; }

        /* Models Grid */
        .models-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(340px, 1fr));
            gap: 45px;
        }
        .car-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 32px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: var(--transition-bounce);
            border: 1px solid rgba(204,0,0,0.2);
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-card);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .car-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -60%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 80%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
            pointer-events: none;
            transform: rotate(25deg);
        }
        .car-card:hover::after {
            opacity: 1;
            animation: shine 0.6s ease-out;
        }
        @keyframes shine {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%) rotate(25deg); }
            100% { transform: translateX(100%) rotate(25deg); }
        }
        .car-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-15px) rotateX(3deg);
            border-color: var(--honda-red);
            box-shadow: var(--box-shadow-glow);
        }
        .car-card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 230px;
            object-fit: contain;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #f5f5f5);
            padding: 25px;
            transition: 0.5s;
        }
        .car-card:hover img { transform: scale(1.05); }
        .car-info { padding: 30px; }
        .car-info h3 { font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .car-info p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .car-price { color: var(--honda-red); font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.25rem; border-top: 2px solid #eee; padding-top: 15px; }

        /* Engine Grid */
        .engine-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(310px, 1fr));
            gap: 35px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }
        .engine-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 30px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #eef2f9;
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .engine-card::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -60%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.3) 0%, rgba(255,255,255,0) 80%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
            pointer-events: none;
            transform: rotate(25deg);
        }
        .engine-card:hover::after {
            opacity: 1;
            animation: shine 0.6s ease-out;
        }
        .engine-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.03) translateY(-8px);
            border-color: var(--honda-red);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 35px rgba(204,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .engine-img-box { height: 210px; overflow: hidden; background: #111; }
        .engine-img-box img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: 0.6s;
        }
        .engine-card:hover .engine-img-box img {
            transform: scale(1.1);
            filter: brightness(1.05);
        }
        .engine-content { padding: 28px; text-align: center; }
        .engine-content h3 { font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 10px; color: var(--honda-red); }
        .engine-content p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #666; line-height: 1.5; }

        /* Tables */
        .table-wrapper {
            overflow-x: auto;
            border-radius: 28px;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; min-width: 700px; }
        th {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a, #2a2a2a, #1a1a1a);
            background-size: 200% 200%;
            animation: gradientMove 3s ease infinite;
            color: white;
            padding: 22px 16px;
            font-family: 'Orbitron';
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        @keyframes gradientMove {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }
        td { padding: 18px 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; text-align: center; transition: 0.2s; }
        tr:hover td { background: rgba(204,0,0,0.05); }
        .spec-label { background: #f8f9fc; font-weight: 700; text-align: left; }

        /* Contact */
        .contact-wrapper {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.6fr;
            gap: 60px;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #fff, #f8f8fc);
            padding: 55px;
            border-radius: 48px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        .contact-info h3 { font-family: 'Orbitron'; font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 28px; }
        .contact-info p { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1rem; }
        .contact-info i { color: var(--honda-red); font-size: 1.4rem; width: 30px; }
        
        input, select, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #eef2f6;
            border-radius: 28px;
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus {
            border-color: var(--honda-red);
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(204,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .btn-submit {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--honda-red), #e60000);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 40px;
            font-family: 'Orbitron';
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .btn-submit:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(204,0,0,0.3);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: #0a0a0a;
            padding: 60px 8% 40px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .social-icons {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 35px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .social-icons a {
            color: #ddd;
            font-size: 2rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .social-icons a:hover {
            color: var(--honda-red);
            transform: translateY(-8px) scale(1.2);
        }
        footer p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 0.9rem; }

        /* Cards fade in */
        .car-card, .engine-card, .history-item {
            opacity: 0;
            animation: cardFadeIn 0.6s ease forwards;
        }
        @keyframes cardFadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        .car-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
        .car-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .car-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
        .car-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .car-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
        .car-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
        .engine-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
        .engine-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
        .engine-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
        .engine-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
        .engine-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.25s; }
        .engine-card:nth-child(6) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .history-item, .contact-wrapper { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 40px; }
            .section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
            .sub-heading { font-size: 1.3rem; }
            .contact-wrapper { padding: 30px; }
            .history-item img { box-shadow: 12px 12px 0 var(--honda-red); }
        }
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .car-card img { height: 180px; }
            .engine-img-box { height: 170px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
    <div class="logo" onclick="showPage('home')">H<span>ONDA</span></div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="#" data-page="home">Ana Sayfa</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" data-page="history">Tarihçe</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" data-page="models">Modeller</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" data-page="engines">Motorlar</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" data-page="compare">Karşılaştırma</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" data-page="contact">İletişim</a></li>
    </ul>
</nav>

<main>
   
    <div id="home" class="page-content active">
        <section class="hero">
            <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/2e2f73_3f4da05190dc4ca4a06a60eb261d5229~mv2.jpeg" alt="Honda" class="hero-bg-img">
            <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
            <h1>HAYALLERİN GÜCÜ</h1>
            <p>The Power of Dreams</p>
            <button onclick="showPage('models')">🚗 KOLEKSİYONU KEŞFET</button>
        </section>
    </div>


    <div id="history" class="page-content">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">TARİHÇEMİZ</h2>
            <div class="history-item">
                <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/2e2f73_fdb36644cc794fecbc785327cba46f93~mv2.png" alt="Soichiro Honda">
                <div class="text-box">
                    <h3>1948: Bir Mühendisin Rüyası</h3>
                    <p>Soichiro Honda (1906–1991), dünyanın en büyük otomotiv ve motosiklet üreticilerinden biri olan Honda Motor Company'nin kurucusu, vizyoner bir mühendis ve sanayicidir. Hayatı ve Kariyerindeki Dönüm Noktaları: Çıraklıktan Atölyeye: 15 yaşında Tokyo'da bir tamirhanede çırak olarak işe başlamış, 6 yıl sonra kendi tamir atölyesini açmıştır. İlk Girişim: 1937'de piston segmanları üretmek için Tokai Seiki şirketini kurmuş; ancak savaş sırasındaki bombardımanlar ve büyük bir deprem sonucu fabrikası yıkılmıştır. Bu işletmeyi Toyota'ya satarak yeni bir başlangıç yapmıştır. Honda'nın Doğuşu: 1946'da bisikletlere küçük jeneratör motorları takma fikriyle Honda Teknik Araştırma Enstitüsü'nü kurmuş, 1948'de ise Takeo Fujisawa ile ortaklaşa Honda Motor Company'yi hayata geçirmiştir. Küresel Başarı: Mühendisliğe olan tutkusu sayesinde Honda'yı dünyanın en büyük motosiklet üreticisi yapmış; ardından otomobil, uçak ve güç ekipmanları alanında küresel bir dev haline getirmiştir.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="history-item">
                <img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/2e2f73_2a84bb09bb81492c8f2cbd706bf4b801~mv2.webp" alt="Honda Racing">
                <div class="text-box">
                    <h3>Yarışçı DNA'sı</h3>
                    <p>Honda için pistler bir laboratuardır. Formula 1'den MotoGP'ye kadar her alanda kazanılan zaferler, bugün kullandığınız otomobillerin güvenliğini ve performansını oluşturur. Honda Racing (HRC), bu tutkunun merkezidir.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

   
    <div id="models" class="page-content">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">MODELLERİMİZ</h2>
            <div class="models-grid">
                <div class="car-card"><img src="https://static.wixstatic.com/media/2e2f73_9e73ed34ddd44d9c885127e9a4b6372b~mv2.jpg" alt="Civic Type R"><div class="car-info"><h3>Civic Type R</h3><p>Pistlerin en hızlı önden çekişli otomobili. 0-100 km/s hızlanması 5.4 saniye, son hızı 275 km/s.</p><p class="car-price">5.500.000 TL'den başlayanlarla</p></div></div>
